name: Borba Cristo
description: Mashup of two ugly monuments from different cities (Borba Gato from São Paulo and Christ the Redeemer from Rio de Janeiro), plus the famous 2008 meme which acquired a new dimension given the neo-Fascist corrupt, incompetent, authoritarian and murderous Bolsonaro government and its purposefully botched and catastrophic management of the Covid pandemic which, among other horrible things, cemented Brazil as a pariah of the world. Locations: -22.951955, -43.210234 and -23.632982, -46.692421. Originally released 1 June 2021 as OBJKT 108885 on HeN.
